<DocHeading Title="Getting started" Level="1" />

<DocHeading Title="Prerequisites" Level="2" />
<p>Havit.Blazor components have the following requirements:</p>
<ul>
	<li>.NET 6.0 or newer (<code>net8.0</code>, <code>net7.0</code> and <code>net6.0</code> multitargeting; <code>net5.0</code> support dropped in v3.2)</li>
	<li>Blazor WebAssembly (preferred) or Blazor Server hosting models (other options at your own risk)</li>
</ul>

