<DocHeading Title="4. Register services" Level="3" />
<p>Add the following line of code to your services registration, typically found in the <code>Program.cs</code> file of your Blazor client project:</p>
<CodeSnippet Language="csharp">builder.Services.AddHxServices();</CodeSnippet>
<p>
	For projects that originated from earlier Blazor templates, these service registrations may be found in the <code>Startup.cs</code> file,
	specifically within the <code>ConfigureServices()</code> method. Note that in this case, you will not use the <code>builder</code>;
	instead, register the services directly to the <code>services</code> collection.
</p>

